Title: Story of a Memorable Victory
Description:
That was a good fight! 

Elder Poa in Iskaara will be interested in listening to the story of that victory.
ObjectivesText: Tell the story of your victory to Elder Poa in Iskaara.
CompletionText:
The most amazing stories might happen with anyone.

Our deeds make us who we are, and I'm always eager to learn of the most impressive acts and make them inspiration to others.
RewardText:
What's that? You have a story for me? Sit down, let me hear it!

<Elder Poa listens to your tale of a victory over a peculiar foe.>

That was thrilling! Thank you for sharing that with me, young one.
